Definition: a card that identifies the bearer as an alien with permanent resident status in the United States
Example: he was surprised to discover that green cards are no longer green
Synonyms: positive_identification, a, card, that, identifies, the, bearer, as, an, alien, with, permanent, resident, status, in, United, States, he, was, surprised, to, discover, green, cards, are, no, longer
Category: noun.communication
